Title: UrlPager
Description:
UrlPager is a custom paging control for asp.net webform application,  It supports url routing and paging through url parameters.  UrlPager requires .Net Framework 3.5 sp1 or higher version.

UrlPager是一个ASP.NET WebForm应用程序中通过url进行分页的分页控件，支持使用url路由来生成自定义的分页url。
